CREATE TABLE [Products] (
    [id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [name] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [model] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [description] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [price] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Products] PRIMARY KEY ([id])
);
ALTER TABLE [Products] ADD [created_on] datetime2 NOT NULL DEFAULT '0001-01-01T00:00:00.0000000';
ALTER TABLE [Products] ADD [isActive] bit NOT NULL DEFAULT CAST(0 AS bit);
ALTER TABLE [Products] ADD [modified_on] datetime2 NOT NULL DEFAULT '0001-01-01T00:00:00.0000000';
ALTER TABLE [Products] ADD [product_price] int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0;
